msgstr "设置或获取 LAN 接口的参数。唯一可检索的参数是 MAC 地址，使用以下方法::"

#: ../../library/network.LAN.rst:75
msgid "The parameters that can be set are:"
msgstr "可以设置的参数是："

#: ../../library/network.LAN.rst:77
msgid "``trace=n`` sets trace levels; suitable values are:"
msgstr "``trace=n`` 设置跟踪级别；适当的值为："

#: ../../library/network.LAN.rst:79
msgid "2: trace TX"
msgstr "2: 跟踪 TX"

