#: ../../library/network.LAN.rst:83
msgid ""
"``low_power=bool`` sets or clears low power mode, valid values being "
"``False`` or ``True``."
msgstr "``low_power=bool`` 设置或清除低功耗模式，有效值为 ``False`` 或 ``True``。"

