msgstr "特定的 LAN 类实现"

#: ../../library/network.LAN.rst:90
msgid ""
"On the mimxrt port, suitable values for the *phy_type* constructor "
"argument are: ``PHY_KSZ8081``, ``PHY_DP83825``, ``PHY_DP83848``, "
"``PHY_LAN8720``, ``PHY_RTL8211F``."
msgstr ""
"在 mimxrt 移植版本上， *phy_type* 构造函数参数的适当值为：``PHY_KSZ8081``, ``PHY_DP83825``, "
"``PHY_DP83848``, ``PHY_LAN8720``, ``PHY_RTL8211F``。"

